<div><div> <a href="/blog/lit-lists/world-literature-todays-75-notable-translations-2022-michelle-johnson" hreflang="und"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/blog/lit-lists/thumbnail-blog-wlt75notable-2022-w.jpg?itok=iPn2OPrR" width="250" height="175" alt="A collage with 10 covers to titles on the 75 Notable Translations list for 2022. " typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />
</a>
</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/lit-lists/world-literature-todays-75-notable-translations-2022-michelle-johnson"><em>World Literature Today’</em>s 75 Notable Translations of 2022
</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/michelle-johnson" hreflang="en">Michelle Johnson</a>
</span></div>
</li>
<li>
